Type Casting : assigning one primitive data type value to another primitive

widening : smaller data type  ==>> larger data type     short(2 bytes) to float(4 bytes)
short s = 12;
float f = s;


narrowing(compressing) :  larger data type ==>> smaller data type      float(4 bytes) to short(2 bytes)

float f = 12.456f;
short s = (short)f;